              5
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Final Inspection</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Verify all debris removal, seal access points, and test system operation. Provide before/after photos and documentation.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </Card>
      </div>
    </div>
